abstract: Liberia's deputy health minister reports that body of unidentified teenager tests positive for Ebola; announcement comes after weeks after World Health Organization declared Liberia Ebola-free.
lead_paragraph: The country’s deputy health minister said the body of a 17-year-old man had tested positive for the disease.

headline.main: Liberia: New Ebola Death Is Reported
headline.print_headline: Africa; Liberia: New Ebola Death Is Reported
